ty of West African States (ECOWAS). Mali is one of 15 (fifteen) members of the regional organization.… August 20, 2020 In "News" The West African bloc ECOWAS will likely decide on Friday whether to lift potentially crippling sanctions imposed on Mali after last month's coup, its mediator said. The mediator, Nigerian former president Goodluck Jonathan, called the 15-nation bloc's sanctions "unfortunate" during a visit to Mali's capital Bamako on Wednesday. West African… September 24, 2020 In "Foreign"